function GetAllCountries(){$.ajax({type:"GET",dataType:"JSON",url:"/Countries/GetCountries",success:function(n){for(var i=$("#getCountryId").val(),r="<option value =''> Select Country <\/option>",t=0;t<n.data.length;t++)r+="<option value="+n.data[t].id+">"+n.data[t].countryName+"<\/option>";$("#countriesDropdown").html(r);$("#countriesDropdown").val(i);i&&GetStatesByCountry(i)},error:function(n){console.log(n)}})}function GetStatesByCountry(n){$.ajax({type:"POST",dataType:"JSON",url:"/States/GetStateByCountry",data:{countryId:n},success:function(t){var r,u,i;for((n||t.data.length>0)&&$("#stateDropdownDiv").show(),r=$("#getStateId").val(),u="<option value=''>Select State <\/option>",i=0;i<t.data.length;i++)u+="<option value="+t.data[i].id+">"+t.data[i].stateName+"<\/option>";$("#stateDropdown").html(u);$("#stateDropdown").val(r);r&&GetCitiesByState(r)},error:function(n){console.log(n)}})}function GetCitiesByState(n){$.ajax({type:"POST",dataType:"JSON",url:"/Cities/GetCityByState",data:{stateId:n},success:function(t){var u,r,i;for((n||t.data.length>0)&&$("#cityDropdownDiv").show(),u=$("#getCityId").val(),r="<option value=''>Select City<\/option>",i=0;i<t.data.length;i++)r+="<option value="+t.data[i].id+">"+t.data[i].cityName+"<\/option>";$("#cityDropdown").html(r);$("#cityDropdown").val(u)},error:function(n){console.log(n)}})}$(document).ready(function(){$("#stateDropdownDiv").hide();$("#cityDropdownDiv").hide();GetAllCountries();$("#countriesDropdown").change(function(){var n=$(this).val();GetStatesByCountry(n)});$("#stateDropdown").change(function(){var n=$(this).val();GetCitiesByState(n)})});